# =============================================================================
# marque — PUBLIC mirror .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# This repository is a one-way public mirror of the private `marque` repo. Its
# job is to serve releases and collect bug/issue reports. This file keeps the
# private repo's internal IP, planning material, and AI/dev tooling out of the
# public tree when content is synced over.
#
# IMPORTANT — gitignore only blocks UNTRACKED files from being committed. It
# cannot protect a file that is REPLACED with a public-specific version
# (CONTRIBUTING.md, README.md) because those are tracked here. Those two must
# additionally be excluded by the mirror-sync step so the dev copy never
# overwrites the public copy. See ".mirror-exclude" for the sync-layer list.
# =============================================================================


# ── Do NOT mirror: internal IP, planning, specs, and AI/dev tooling ──────────
# Everything below is private. None of it belongs in the public mirror.
/.specify/
/specs/
/docs/plans/
/claudedocs/
/site/

# Editor / AI assistant tooling and configs
/.vscode/
/.claude/
/.gemini/
/.autopilot/
/.jules/
/.mcp.json
/.mcp.json.license
/contextlint.config.json
/contextlint.config.json.license

# Internal docs and agreements (CONTRIBUTING/README are handled below — they
# are REPLACED, not dropped, so they are intentionally NOT listed here).
/CLA.md
/CLAUDE.md
/AGENTS.md
/GEMINI.md

# Public-specific replacements (TRACKED here, never overwritten by the sync):
#   - /CONTRIBUTING.md  → "not accepting contributions; suggest via issues"
#   - /README.md        → public placeholder until the first public release
# These are deliberately absent from the ignore list. The mirror-sync step
# (not this file) is responsible for not copying the dev versions over them.


# ── .github/: allowlist only the public surface ─────────────────────────────
# Everything under .github is internal/dev by default. Only the public release
# + assurance workflows and the issue templates are published. Anything new the
# private repo adds under .github (speckit agents/prompts, gemini commands,
# claude.yml, codeql, bench/throughput/gramine workflows, the dev ci.yml,
# CODEOWNERS, dependabot, FUNDING, PR template) is ignored automatically.
/.github/*
!/.github/workflows
!/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE
/.github/workflows/*
!/.github/workflows/release.yml
!/.github/workflows/assurance.yml


# =============================================================================
# Standard build artifacts, caches, and OS noise (carried from the dev repo)
# =============================================================================

*.local.toml
*.env

# Caches
[Cc]ache/
.[Cc]ache/

# masking-pin-lint cache is intentionally tracked: D11 in the engine-rule
# refactor decisions requires daily-refreshed cache files committed to the repo
# so CI's cache-with-fallback path has data even when GitHub's API is
# unreachable. The negation below carves that directory out of the generic
# [Cc]ache/ rule above.
!tools/masking-pin-lint/cache/
!tools/masking-pin-lint/cache/**

# proptest persistent failure seeds are intentionally tracked. Each
# `*.proptest-regressions` file carries the seed of a real property-test
# failure; checking them in makes the seed part of CI so the same input is
# re-tried before any new shrink work. Do NOT add `*.proptest-regressions`
# to this file.

# Python bytecode (tools/perf/ and a few scripts are Python; running them
# locally creates __pycache__/ directories).
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Packages
node_modules/
.venv/

# Build artifacts
target/
dist/
crates/**/generated/
debug/
.astro/
.wrangler/

*.spdx
*:Zone.Identifier

# General
nohup.out
.Trash-*
.nfs*
.fuse_hidden*
[._]*.un~
*~
[._]*.sw[a-p][a-p]
Session.vim
Sessionx.vim
*.lnk
$RECYCLE.BIN/
Thumbs*
*.pdb
**/*.rs.bk
.cursorignore
.cursorindexingignore
.directory
[Dd]esktop.ini
*.stackdump
.AppleDB
.AppleDesktop
Network Trash Folder
Temporary Items
.apdisk
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.fseventsd
.Spotlight-V100
.TemporaryItems
.Trashes
.VolumeIcons.icns
.com.apple.timemachine.donotpresent
._*
.history
.history/
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon[*]

# Worktrees
worktrees/
.worktrees/
